      <title>Brightmoon, The Magical Witch Girl</title>
      <author> sowerbot </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1232808/brightmoon-the-magical-witch-girl/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1232808-brightmoon-the-magical-witch-girl/chapter/1232862/#comments</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">a98757eaeaa8401664c47891e8b689bcb1060687</guid>
