      <title>Hazel and the Attic</title>
      <author> Violet_Velvet </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1265919/hazel-and-the-attic/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1265919-hazel-and-the-attic/chapter/1265921/#comments</comments>
